data.title: Martin J Taylor
data.meta_description: Enlisted August 1966. Went through the Depot in 310 plt. Posted to 1 Para. 310,311 and 312 platoon formed B coy 1Para. Posted to Aden May 67, Northern Ireland 69 and 70. Seconded to 44 Brigade HQ 1970 to 1973. Demobbed June 1973.
data.text:
Enlisted August 1966. Went through the Depot in 310 plt. Posted to 1 Para. 310,311 and 312 platoon formed B coy 1Para. Posted to Aden May 67, Northern Ireland 69 and 70.

Seconded to 44 Brigade HQ 1970 to 1973. Demobbed June 1973.
